headline: Eaton Announces $18.5M Expansion of Orchard Park, New York Aerospace Manufacturing Facility
summary: BUFFALO, N.Y., May 08, 2025--Intelligent power management company Eaton today announced the expansion of its Orchard Park, N.Y., facility to support growing demand for the aerospace mission systems solutions manufactured at the site. The $18.5 million investment will significantly increase production capacity to serve growing demand by military defense, commercial aerospace and space customers and add 77 skilled manufacturing jobs to the community.
